### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
Bioinformatic and actionscript project which helps to retrieve gene information.Interactive user can be able to select the desired fields and results can be download as a CSV

```
$ cd your_repo_root/Popgenie-Bulktools
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
